@UnitConversion.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5012

### List supported categories
GET {{UnitConversion.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/categories
Accept: application/json

### List units for a category
GET {{UnitConversion.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/categories/Length/units
Accept: application/json

### Convert via POST (JSON body)
POST {{UnitConversion.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/conversions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "value": 100,
  "fromUnit": "km",
  "toUnit": "mi"
}

### Convert via GET (query string)
GET {{UnitConversion.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/conversions?value=100&from=C&to=F
Accept: application/json

###
